Title: Guess EDT - 50 ml(For Men)
Description: Playful yet resolute, a note of youthful tranquillity characterises the Guess Man. The fresh, clean aroma of this luxury perfume leads you down an exciting trail through notes reminiscent of lush green foliage after the rains. Earthy, like the woody bark of an ancient tree and crisp, like the taste of the bracing sea breeze on your tongue, the myriad notes of the dynamic Guess Eau de Toilette are artistically united by the skillful hands of perfumer Steve Demercado. Guess Man opens with a citrusy top note of bergamot, Granny Smith apples and a refreshing hint of ozone. Spicy notes of white pepper, ginger, and nutmeg mingle with soft lavender in the heart note to create an appealing balance of aromas. The warm base note of sandalwood, spiced amber, blue fir, Peru balm and suede leather mingle with velvety musk to perfectly complement the top and heart notes with its underlying note of decisive masculinity. The scent is an impeccable accessory for the immaculately dressed contemporary man. With Guess Man you certainly get to wear your attitude.

Title: Perry Ellis Reserve EDP  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: She’s the quiet girl who reads alone at the downtown coffee shop - radiating a serene and cerebral quality. A woman of today with an endearing shyness, she masks more than she reveals just like a whiff of Perry Ellis Reserve. Created by Jean-Louis Grauby, this enchanting Eau De Parfum is made for the established house of Perry Ellis. Zesty notes of ginger along with rich hints of sandalwood, earthy hints of patchouli, peppery and refreshing extracts of freesia, powdery flecks of violet, organic notes of oakmoss, intense and sweet hints of rose, hay-toned marigold and warming notes of chamomile. The intoxicating array of aromatic extracts ensure that this oriental floral fragrance is perfect for that night you’ve been waiting for. This fragrance comes in a slender cylindrical flacon that radiates a pale green hue of pistachio. A transparent spherical stopper of this fragrance acts as the simple finishing touch. A spritz of this scent and embrace everything life has to offer.

Title: Chris Adams Stunner Pour Homme Eau de Parfum  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: A fragrant perfume of citric tones, balanced by a bold pepper and amber. The bottle is tinted gold, with black leather detailing. Chris Adams Stunner pour homme 10ml Eau parfum Top Notes: Citrus fruits, Bergamot Middle Notes: Lavender, Pepper Base Notes: Musk

Description: A fragrance designed for the emotional intelligent Personality. It is for a quietly confdent personality who is caring and understanding.
